channel.title: IPconfig?
channel.description:
for whatever reason my "ipconfig" doesnt work in the cmd. i also tried ipconfig/all...nothing.. also now, non of my run.bat works... i have to use this one, and its only one that works.. even then it runs at 10% regular, holds only around 10 people now.. it used to hold 35+ no lagg..
[code]@echo off title Java Compiler and Runner "C:/Program Files/Java/jdk1.6.0_04/bin/javac.exe" *.java "C:/Program Files/Java/jdk1.6.0_04/bin/java.exe" server pause[/code]
thats the only run.bat that works.[br][br][size=1]Posted on: March 02, 2008, 01:16:08 PM[/size][hr][code]Microsoft Windows XP [Version 5.1.2600] (C) Copyright 1985-2001 Microsoft Corp.
C:\Documents and Settings\Lorena>ipconfig 'ipconfig' is not recognized as an internal or external command, operable program or batch file.
C:\Documents and Settings\Lorena>[/code]
